description:
&lt;p&gt;We are a friendly, supportive and forward thinking London practice, which provides primary care services to a mixed demographic population of just over 10,000 patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are now looking to recruit a dynamic and proactive full time Advanced Nurse Practitioner who can join our established &amp; friendly team and work collaboratively within the multi-disciplinary general practice team, providing support to the GP’s and practice team as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a developing role and would therefore, suit someone who can take an active part in developing and building this service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an experienced advanced nurse practitioner, you’ll be a vital addition to our clinical team and you should be comfortable in assessing, diagnosing, treating and discharging patients autonomously every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Together with the rest of the nursing team, you will be responsible for providing an excellent standard of patient care and health promotion to all who access our care services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prescribing is an essential requirement and career development is encouraged.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information, please contact the Practice Manager on 020 7476 2255&lt;/p&gt;
